; Coverage for report.cc COMMAND break statements:
; Lines (p), (r), (s), (t), (x)
; Unknown commands whose first letter matches a COMMAND case but whose
; name does not match any known command hit the break statement.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food  $10.00
    Assets:Cash

; 'peel' starts with 'p' but is not p/print/prices/pricedb/pricesdb/pricemap/payees -> break 1799
test peel -> 1
__ERROR__
Error: Unrecognized command 'peel'
end test

